动物</h1><nav class=\"thlex-index\"><ul>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.1\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.1\">2.1 洁净的动物（申14:4–6）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.2\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.2\">2.2 羚羊（antelope）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.3\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.3\">2.3 猿猴（apes）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.4\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.4\">2.4 驴（ass, donkey）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.5\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.5\">2.5 蝙蝠（bat）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.6\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.6\">2.6 熊（bear）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.7\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.7\">2.7 北非狷羚（狍子）（bubal hartebeest [roe deer]）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.8\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.8\">2.8 骆驼、独峰驼（camel, dromedary）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.9\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.9\">2.9 猫（cat）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.10\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.10\">2.10 牛、母牛、阉牛、公牛（cattle, cow, ox, bull）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.11\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.11\">2.11 鹿（deer）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.12\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.12\">2.12 狗（dog）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.13\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.13\">2.13 儒艮（dugong）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.14\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.14\">2.14 象（elephant）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.15\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.15\">2.15 瞪羚（gazelle）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.16\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.16\">2.16 山羊（goat）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.17\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.17\">2.17 野兔、兔子（hare）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.18\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.18\">2.18 马（horse）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.19\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.19\">2.19 鬣狗（hyena）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.20\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.20\">2.20 蹄兔、石獾（hyrax, rock badger）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.21\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.21\">2.21 野山羊、羱羊、高山山羊（ibex, wild goat, mountain goat）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.22\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.22\">2.22 土狼、豺狼、野狗、狐狸（jackal, fox）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.23\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.23\">2.23 金钱豹、猎豹（leopard, cheetah）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.24\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.24\">2.24 狮子（lion）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.25\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.25\">2.25 田鼠（mole rat）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.26\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.26\">2.26 獴、鼬鼠（mongoose, weasel）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.27\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.27\">2.27 老鼠、耗子（mouse, rat）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.28\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.28\">2.28 骡子（mule）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.29\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.29\">2.29 羚羊、长角羚、剑羚（oryx）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.30\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.30\">2.30 猪（pig）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.31\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.31\">2.31 绵羊、羔羊、小羊（sheep, lamb）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.32\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.32\">2.32 野驴（wild ass）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.33\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.33\">2.33 野猪（wild boar）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.34\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.34\">2.34 野牛（wild ox）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:2.35\" href=\"#FAUNA:2.35\">2.35 狼（wolf）</a></li>\n</ul></nav>",
